        <dc:title>Reinforcement Learning: An Overview</dc:title>
        <dcterms:abstract>This manuscript gives a big-picture, up-to-date overview of the field of (deep) reinforcement learning and sequential decision making, covering value-based methods, policy-based methods, model-based methods, multi-agent RL, LLMs and RL, and various other topics (e.g., offline RL, hierarchical RL, intrinsic reward). It also includes some code snippets for training LLMs with RL.</dcterms:abstract>
